{"tid":1947964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不服來辯，MyTV Super「機場特警」有得煲","createTime":"2020-03-28T15:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T06:37:27.000Z","uid":262329,"like":76,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4886ed009d93dc78937175c19110130fe750c5","tid":1947964,"uid":262329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"希望唔好屌我做標題黨住，大家屋企因為裝寬頻而送咗部無撚用嘅MyTV Super？會唔會已經掉撚咗或者賣咗？如果你未掉嘅話，請花少少時間同我睇曬佢。<br />\n<br />\n大家其實知唔知其實<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">MyTV Super 係要還架？<br />\nMyTV Super 係要還架！<br />\nMyTV Super 係要還架！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n有無聽過以下對白？<br />\n「MyTV Super 送比你嘅，完咗約（寬頻）都唔洗還。」<br />\n「部機（MyTV Super）如果唔用嘅話直接掉咗佢就得。」<br />\n「唔用咪比朋友囉，可能佢地啱用呢。」<br />\n<br />\n等我話比大家知真正嘅故事：<br />\n當你登記一個寬頻、電話服務，而該服務如果會「送」MyTV Super 比你嘅話，伏已中。<span style=\"color: orange;\">因為喺你Say Yes 嘅一刻，公司已經將你嘅個人資料完完整整咁Send 咗一個Copy 比CCTVB，之後會再去到咩機構嘅手上，真係不敢想像。</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>點證實？</strong></ins><br />\n打去CCTVB 23 999 666<br />\n㩒1字<br />\n㩒2字<br />\n之後入自己電話號碼<br />\n如果Pass 到，即係話你嘅個人資料已經不知不覺間送咗比CCTVB！如果佢話你輸入嘅資料無效，即係話你安全。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>咁點算？</ins></strong><br />\n入咗自己電話號碼之後㩒8字聯絡客戶服務，之後同佢講，要求佢將你嘅個人資料從佢地個Database 入面刪除，當收到呢個要求，CCTVB 就會要求你先將垃圾MyTV Super 機頂盒歸還，還咗先會刪除！<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>咁點還？</strong></ins><br />\n兩個地址：<br />\n1. 灣仔軒尼斯道395-399號東區商業中心14樓04室<br />\n2. 尖沙咀星光行中座14樓27室<br />\n星期一至星期六 11am - 7:30pm<br />\n星期日 12nn - 6:00pm<br />\n還完之後打番去CCTVB 同佢講話垃圾機頂盒已經歸還，要求佢將你嘅個人資料刪除，兩星期之後打番去同一個電話，做多一次測試，就會知道對方有無真係刪除到。<br />\n<br />\n整過個程係有啲煩嘅，但諗起「趙家賢跌了一隻耳仔」，諗起呢九個月以黎呢個垃圾電視台點樣偏頗，呢幾年以黎報道咗幾多假嘅新聞，花你一個半個鐘時間去對付佢，咁簡單嘅事情，一齊做低佢啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好掉，還撚咗佢啊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oUYGP8F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoUYGP8F.png&h=7b614062&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26ccfc3cc40dcee8ed603239bd01f5bbdecb3f98","tid":1947964,"uid":262329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"自己推1"},{"pid":"5f12f32cedec580b52e3e0752b1f588333021b47","tid":1947964,"uid":203431,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T15:50:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">講正經野正正經經打個標題唔撚得<br />\n係要做標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚反感</span>"},{"pid":"bbcc5b7e01fbb0c3c7dbb5ab3ef95345c3eacbb4","tid":1947964,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"雖然冇用過唔明，不過機場黑警見到都覺得臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[有片、少圖] 2019年黑警虐待市民暴行紀錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1947342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1947342</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f3b2772d4a17555dc735358bceef44c2aaa8ea59","tid":1947964,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T15:52:37.000Z","msg":"要樣樣野都好似佢咁玩大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=c9T6KNSJFlg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc9T6KNSJFlg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=313359f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=c9T6KNSJFlg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"73061044f90dac1b1d2c0dd6548955dbc62346b5","tid":1947964,"uid":10881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb90881aff8f4d33b502bc782146fdc30c269d89","tid":1947964,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime